# azure-cloud-services Reference

This directory contains 19 icons extracted from `azure-cloud-services.excalidrawlib`.

| Icon Name              | Filename                            |
| ---------------------- | ----------------------------------- |
| Active Directory       | `icons/Active-Directory.json`       |
| App Service            | `icons/App-Service.json`            |
| Application Insights   | `icons/Application-Insights.json`   |
| Azure DevOps           | `icons/Azure-DevOps.json`           |
| Azure logo             | `icons/Azure-logo.json`             |
| Blob Storage           | `icons/Blob-Storage.json`           |
| Data Lake              | `icons/Data-Lake.json`              |
| Disk                   | `icons/Disk.json`                   |

| PS Runbook             | `icons/PS-Runbook.json`             |

| Resource Group         | `icons/Resource-Group.json`         |

| Service Bus Namespace  | `icons/Service-Bus-Namespace.json`  |

| Virtual Network        | `icons/Virtual-Network.json`        |

## Usage

Each icon JSON file contains the complete `elements` array needed to render that icon in Excalidraw.
You can copy the elements from these files into your Excalidraw diagrams.
